    "body": "For the record, the reason we do this is that source names with duplicated content can lead to weird compilation errors in some scenarios. This doesn't happen with `forge build` because in that case remappings are used, but Hardhat resolves the remappings itself.\r\n\r\nBut we should re-visit this, it might be unnecessarily limiting.",
